                        "AcquisitionStrategy": {
                            "val": "The OPF will be an evolutionary acquisition program to incrementally develop and deliver a vendor provided munition capable of destroying multiple target sets.  OPF will be integrated with a government developed and owned mounting platform and command and control system.  This strategy will allow the program office to procure munitions from multiple vendors resulting in reduced costs.  This strategy will also allow the program office to focus future efforts on development of munitions that are vehicle and C2 agnostic."
                        },
